'''Codruese''' was the official language of [[Munto Codru/Legends|Munto Codru]] and was spoken by the native [[Codru-Ji]] [[Species/Legends|species]].<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" /> The younger Codru-Ji, under the shape of [[Wyrwulf|Wyrwulves]], could not speak this language, but they could understand it.

Codruese used snarls, whines and throaty barks, as well as some other canine noises. Codruese also had a complex lexicon and many idioms, making it a difficult language.<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

